<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:11
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='448' id='t-448'>I'm going to go off script</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1715' id='t-1715'>and make Chris quite nervous here</span>
